values:
Fights, boyfriend-stealing, backstabing, name calling.
Ahhh, wow.  school is so exciting. Screw class rooms and education, its all about the students.  The girls, the boys, who's with who, what parties are coming up, what's going on with that girls outfit... 
WHO CARES!!! ... well, ill tell you who.  Everyone! everyone's so wrapped up in the social aspect, that it doesnt even seem like people care about their studies.  For example, grade 12 history students, including myself, are all worked up about the dance, their outfits, who their dates are... meanwhile, we have a project and a test on monday AND for those who arent caught up in their work, an other project FOR TOMORROW
... fuck

a day in the life of a Hanmer High senior student,

Stephanie

star light, star bright
the first star i see tonight
i wish i may, i wish i might,
have this wish i wish tonight....

I wish my school principal wasnt so boring and strict
I wish there were more things to do in Sudbury for those under 19
I wish Justin wasnt such a bitch, and would go to his classes
I wish Kristal would leave my mom alone
I wish history tests never existed
I wish i was a princess, and had lots of money

finally, I wish lunch would come around soon!!!


love ya bitches and hoes,
Pimp master Stephizle

->werd
